[
  {
    "start": 0.08,
    "end": 7.2,
    "text": "I'm 103 years old and I'm about to tell",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 4.16,
    "end": 10.88,
    "text": "you something that nobody, not your",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 7.2,
    "end": 15.04,
    "text": "parents, not your therapist, not your",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 10.88,
    "end": 18.16,
    "text": "self-help books will ever tell you. And",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 15.04,
    "end": 23.359,
    "text": "the reason they won't because it's too",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 18.16,
    "end": 26.72,
    "text": "painful, too stark, too real. I've been",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 23.359,
    "end": 30.64,
    "text": "alive for over a century. I've buried",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 26.72,
    "end": 34.719,
    "text": "three husbands, two children, most of my",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 30.64,
    "end": 38.239,
    "text": "friends, and every single person I knew",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 34.719,
    "end": 42.64,
    "text": "before I turned 40. I've watched the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 38.239,
    "end": 46.239,
    "text": "world transform four times over. And in",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 42.64,
    "end": 49.76,
    "text": "all that time, I've learned one truth",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 46.239,
    "end": 52.879,
    "text": "that haunts me every single day.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 49.76,
    "end": 56.64,
    "text": "We're all living like we have forever",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 52.879,
    "end": 59.12,
    "text": "when we barely have anything at all. But",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 56.64,
    "end": 60.239,
    "text": "let me tell you when I actually learned",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 59.12,
    "end": 66.64,
    "text": "this, ",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 60.239,
    "end": 69.92,
    "text": "not at 90, not at 80, at 33 years old.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 66.64,
    "end": 72.799,
    "text": "And it took me 70 years to fully",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 69.92,
    "end": 77.6,
    "text": "understand what that moment was trying",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 72.799,
    "end": 80.08,
    "text": "to teach me. It was 1955,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 77.6,
    "end": 81.119,
    "text": "October 14th.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 80.08,
    "end": 84.24,
    "text": "I remember ",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 81.119,
    "end": 86.96,
    "text": "because it was a Friday, and I'd been",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 84.24,
    "end": 90.64,
    "text": "planning to go dancing that weekend with",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 86.96,
    "end": 94.4,
    "text": "my husband, Robert. We'd been married",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 90.64,
    "end": 96.32,
    "text": "eight years. Had two little boys, James",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 94.4,
    "end": 99.439,
    "text": "and William.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 96.32,
    "end": 103.04,
    "text": "Robert worked at the steel mill. good",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 99.439,
    "end": 105.52,
    "text": "man, steady, the kind who'd kiss my",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 103.04,
    "end": 108.56,
    "text": "forehead every morning before he left",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 105.52,
    "end": 110.32,
    "text": "for work and say, \"See you tonight,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 108.56,
    "end": 114.32,
    "text": "Dorothy.\"",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 110.32,
    "end": 117.52,
    "text": "Except that Friday, he didn't come home.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 114.32,
    "end": 120.799,
    "text": "There was an accident at the mill. They",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 117.52,
    "end": 122.32,
    "text": "said it was quick. They said he didn't",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 120.799,
    "end": 125.84,
    "text": "suffer.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 122.32,
    "end": 129.039,
    "text": "But they always say that, don't they?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 125.84,
    "end": 133.28,
    "text": "What they didn't say, what nobody tells",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 129.039,
    "end": 136.4,
    "text": "you is that when someone dies suddenly,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 133.28,
    "end": 141.599,
    "text": "they take all your unsaid words with",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 136.4,
    "end": 145.599,
    "text": "them. Every I love you, you didn't say.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 141.599,
    "end": 148.64,
    "text": "Every fight you didn't apologize for.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 145.599,
    "end": 155.04,
    "text": "Every moment you were too busy or too",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 148.64,
    "end": 157.12,
    "text": "tired or too angry to just be present.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 155.04,
    "end": 161.36,
    "text": "That night, sitting at our kitchen",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 157.12,
    "end": 164.56,
    "text": "table, I made a promise to myself.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 161.36,
    "end": 167.92,
    "text": "I promised I would never waste another",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 164.56,
    "end": 169.76,
    "text": "day. I promised I would live",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 167.92,
    "end": 174.239,
    "text": "intentionally,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 169.76,
    "end": 175.76,
    "text": "love openly, and never postpone joy",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 174.239,
    "end": 179.36,
    "text": "again.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 175.76,
    "end": 181.92,
    "text": "And you know what? I broke that promise",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 179.36,
    "end": 185.28,
    "text": "almost immediately.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 181.92,
    "end": 189.28,
    "text": "Oh, I thought I was living better. I",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 185.28,
    "end": 192.959,
    "text": "hugged my boys more. I said, \"I love you",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 189.28,
    "end": 197.12,
    "text": "more often.\" But then life happens,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 192.959,
    "end": 202.08,
    "text": "doesn't it? I remarried, got busy with",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 197.12,
    "end": 205.28,
    "text": "work, the boys grew up. I told myself I",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 202.08,
    "end": 210.4,
    "text": "was doing fine, that I'd learned my",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 205.28,
    "end": 212.959,
    "text": "lesson. But I hadn't. Not really.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 210.4,
    "end": 215.2,
    "text": "Because here's what I didn't understand",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 212.959,
    "end": 218.879,
    "text": "at 33.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 215.2,
    "end": 220.64,
    "text": "What took me another 70 years to fully",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 218.879,
    "end": 224.0,
    "text": "grasp.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 220.64,
    "end": 227.04,
    "text": "It's not enough to survive tragedy and",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 224.0,
    "end": 229.76,
    "text": "tell yourself you've changed.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 227.04,
    "end": 232.959,
    "text": "The real lesson isn't that life is",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 229.76,
    "end": 237.04,
    "text": "short. Every greeting card tells you",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 232.959,
    "end": 238.72,
    "text": "that. The real lesson is that you will",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 237.04,
    "end": 242.4,
    "text": "forget.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 238.72,
    "end": 245.28,
    "text": "You will slip back into autopilot.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 242.4,
    "end": 249.28,
    "text": "You will start believing you have time",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 245.28,
    "end": 253.28,
    "text": "again.  And that forgetting, that",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 249.28,
    "end": 256.88,
    "text": "slow drift back into complacency,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 253.28,
    "end": 259.6,
    "text": "that's the real tragedy. I married again",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 256.88,
    "end": 261.12,
    "text": "in 1958.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 259.6,
    "end": 265.919,
    "text": "Charles,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 261.12,
    "end": 268.96,
    "text": "sweet man. We had 42 years together",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 265.919,
    "end": 271.68,
    "text": "before his heart gave out.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 268.96,
    "end": 274.32,
    "text": "And you know, my biggest regret about",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 271.68,
    "end": 277.84,
    "text": "those 42 years, ",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 274.32,
    "end": 281.04,
    "text": "not the fights we had, not the money",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 277.84,
    "end": 285.199,
    "text": "troubles or the disagreements. ",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 281.04,
    "end": 288.858,
    "text": "My biggest regret is all the ordinary",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 285.199,
    "end": 291.84,
    "text": "Tuesday nights I spent doing laundry",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 288.858,
    "end": 295.52,
    "text": " instead of sitting with him.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 291.84,
    "end": 298.16,
    "text": "All the times I said, \"Not now. I'm",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 295.52,
    "end": 302.32,
    "text": "busy.\"  when he wanted to take a",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 298.16,
    "end": 305.12,
    "text": "walk. All the moments I treated like",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 302.32,
    "end": 308.0,
    "text": "they were guaranteed. ",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 305.12,
    "end": 311.28,
    "text": "Because here's what nobody tells you",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 308.0,
    "end": 315.36,
    "text": "about living to be my age.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 311.28,
    "end": 318.88,
    "text": "You don't just lose the people you love.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 315.36,
    "end": 320.72,
    "text": "You lose them over and over again in",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 318.88,
    "end": 323.759,
    "text": "your memory.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 320.72,
    "end": 327.52,
    "text": "Every time you think about them, you",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 323.759,
    "end": 329.68,
    "text": "remember another moment you wasted.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 327.52,
    "end": 334.0,
    "text": "Another conversation",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 329.68,
    "end": 337.52,
    "text": "you were too distracted to fully hear.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 334.0,
    "end": 341.84,
    "text": "Another hug you cut short because you",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 337.52,
    "end": 344.88,
    "text": "had somewhere to be. My son William died",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 341.84,
    "end": 348.96,
    "text": "in 1987.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 344.88,
    "end": 351.52,
    "text": "45 years old, cancer.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 348.96,
    "end": 355.12,
    "text": "I was 65.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 351.52,
    "end": 358.8,
    "text": "I remember sitting by his hospital bed",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 355.12,
    "end": 364.0,
    "text": "holding his hand and he said to me,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 358.8,
    "end": 366.88,
    "text": "\"Mom, I'm sorry I didn't call more.\"",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 364.0,
    "end": 370.56,
    "text": "And I wanted to scream.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 366.88,
    "end": 373.68,
    "text": "I wanted to shake him and say, \"Why are",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 370.56,
    "end": 376.639,
    "text": "we apologizing now?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 373.68,
    "end": 378.88,
    "text": "Why didn't we call each other every day",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 376.639,
    "end": 382.639,
    "text": "when we could?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 378.88,
    "end": 387.44,
    "text": "But I didn't say that. I just held his",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 382.639,
    "end": 389.039,
    "text": "hand and lied. I said we had enough",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 387.44,
    "end": 392.96,
    "text": "time.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 389.039,
    "end": 397.68,
    "text": "We didn't. My third husband, Frank, died",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 392.96,
    "end": 401.6,
    "text": "two years ago, 98 years old. We'd been",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 397.68,
    "end": 404.639,
    "text": "together 21 years. And even after",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 401.6,
    "end": 409.039,
    "text": "everything I'd learned, everything I'd",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 404.639,
    "end": 411.84,
    "text": "lost, you know what I still did? I still",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 409.039,
    "end": 414.96,
    "text": "sometimes scrolled through my phone",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 411.84,
    "end": 418.16,
    "text": "while  he was talking. I still",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 414.96,
    "end": 421.759,
    "text": "sometimes sighed when he told the same",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 418.16,
    "end": 424.8,
    "text": "story for the 10th time. I still",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 421.759,
    "end": 426.319,
    "text": "sometimes thought, \"I'll pay attention",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 424.8,
    "end": 429.36,
    "text": "tomorrow.\"",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 426.319,
    "end": 431.599,
    "text": "There wasn't always a tomorrow. ",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 429.36,
    "end": 434.24,
    "text": "You're young. You're sitting there",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 431.599,
    "end": 437.199,
    "text": "thinking, \"This is depressing.\"",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 434.24,
    "end": 438.88,
    "text": "Thinking, \"Well,  everyone dies",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 437.199,
    "end": 441.84,
    "text": "eventually.\"",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 438.88,
    "end": 444.88,
    "text": "But you're missing the point. The point",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 441.84,
    "end": 447.199,
    "text": "isn't that everyone dies.  The",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 444.88,
    "end": 450.659,
    "text": "point is that you're acting like you're",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 447.199,
    "end": 453.28,
    "text": "the exception, like somehow your life",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 450.659,
    "end": 456.0,
    "text": " will be different, like you'll",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 453.28,
    "end": 457.68,
    "text": "have time later to live the way you want",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 456.0,
    "end": 461.919,
    "text": "to live.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 457.68,
    "end": 465.759,
    "text": "I'm 103 years old and I can tell you",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 461.919,
    "end": 469.12,
    "text": "with absolute certainty later never",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 465.759,
    "end": 472.24,
    "text": "comes. You think you'll travel when you",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 469.12,
    "end": 475.52,
    "text": "retire.  Your knees will be shot",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 472.24,
    "end": 478.8,
    "text": "by then. You think you'll reconnect with",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 475.52,
    "end": 482.56,
    "text": "your sister after this busy period at",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 478.8,
    "end": 485.36,
    "text": "work. That busy period will last 20",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 482.56,
    "end": 485.84,
    "text": "years and then she'll be gone.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 485.36,
    "end": 488.0,
    "text": " ",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 485.84,
    "end": 490.879,
    "text": " You think you'll start writing that",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 488.0,
    "end": 493.44,
    "text": "book, learning that language, ",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 490.879,
    "end": 494.96,
    "text": "taking that trip, having that",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 493.44,
    "end": 498.4,
    "text": "conversation",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 494.96,
    "end": 499.12,
    "text": "when you have more time, more money,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 498.4,
    "end": 503.12,
    "text": "more ",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 499.12,
    "end": 507.52,
    "text": "whatever. You won't. Because here's the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 503.12,
    "end": 510.25,
    "text": "cruel joke. You do have time right now.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 507.52,
    "end": 512.24,
    "text": "You just don't value it correctly.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 510.25,
    "end": 515.36,
    "text": " You trade it for things that",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 512.24,
    "end": 518.24,
    "text": "don't matter. You spend it on people who",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 515.36,
    "end": 521.279,
    "text": "drain you. You  waste it worrying",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 518.24,
    "end": 522.479,
    "text": "about things that won't matter in 5",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 521.279,
    "end": 525.36,
    "text": "years. ",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 522.479,
    "end": 528.48,
    "text": "And then one day, if you're lucky enough",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 525.36,
    "end": 531.519,
    "text": "to live as long as I have, you'll look",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 528.48,
    "end": 535.519,
    "text": "back and realize  you had all the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 531.519,
    "end": 537.839,
    "text": "time you needed. You just didn't use it.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 535.519,
    "end": 540.64,
    "text": "I'm not telling you to quit your job and",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 537.839,
    "end": 542.56,
    "text": "run off to  find yourself.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 540.64,
    "end": 544.72,
    "text": "I'm not saying ignore your",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 542.56,
    "end": 548.24,
    "text": "responsibilities.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 544.72,
    "end": 551.68,
    "text": "I'm saying something much harder.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 548.24,
    "end": 555.6,
    "text": "I'm saying pay  attention",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 551.68,
    "end": 560.399,
    "text": "right now, today, to  what you're",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 555.6,
    "end": 562.64,
    "text": "actually doing with your one brief, unre",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 560.399,
    "end": 566.24,
    "text": "repeatable life.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 562.64,
    "end": 571.519,
    "text": "Your grandmother, is she still alive?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 566.24,
    "end": 574.48,
    "text": "Call her today. Not tomorrow, today.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 571.519,
    "end": 576.959,
    "text": "Because I'm a grandmother and I can tell",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 574.48,
    "end": 580.88,
    "text": "you exactly  what she's doing",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 576.959,
    "end": 584.399,
    "text": "right now. She's sitting somewhere,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 580.88,
    "end": 588.0,
    "text": "maybe looking at old photos, maybe just",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 584.399,
    "end": 590.72,
    "text": "staring out a window and she's thinking",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 588.0,
    "end": 592.399,
    "text": "about all the people who don't call",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 590.72,
    "end": 596.72,
    "text": "anymore,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 592.399,
    "end": 600.08,
    "text": "all the grandchildren who are too busy.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 596.72,
    "end": 603.279,
    "text": "and she's telling herself it's okay,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 600.08,
    "end": 605.839,
    "text": "that everyone has their own lives, that",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 603.279,
    "end": 608.72,
    "text": "she understands.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 605.839,
    "end": 610.88,
    "text": "But it breaks her heart a little more",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 608.72,
    "end": 613.6,
    "text": "each day.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 610.88,
    "end": 616.48,
    "text": "Your parents, if you're lucky enough to",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 613.6,
    "end": 620.16,
    "text": "still have them, they're not going to be",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 616.48,
    "end": 622.64,
    "text": "here forever. And when they're gone,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 620.16,
    "end": 625.532,
    "text": "you're not going to care about that",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 622.64,
    "end": 626.0,
    "text": "argument you had 5 years ago.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 625.532,
    "end": 628.24,
    "text": " ",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 626.0,
    "end": 631.2,
    "text": " You're not going to care that they were",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 628.24,
    "end": 633.92,
    "text": "difficult sometimes  or that they",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 631.2,
    "end": 636.88,
    "text": "didn't understand you.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 633.92,
    "end": 640.64,
    "text": "You're going to care about all the phone",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 636.88,
    "end": 642.959,
    "text": "calls you didn't make, all the visits",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 640.64,
    "end": 645.839,
    "text": "you postponed,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 642.959,
    "end": 649.2,
    "text": "all the times you could have just sat",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 645.839,
    "end": 652.387,
    "text": "with them  and didn't.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 649.2,
    "end": 654.079,
    "text": "I know this because I am that parent",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 652.387,
    "end": 656.56,
    "text": " now.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 654.079,
    "end": 660.16,
    "text": "I had two sons. ",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 656.56,
    "end": 660.8,
    "text": "William died 38 years ago.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 660.16,
    "end": 666.88,
    "text": "James ",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 660.8,
    "end": 671.36,
    "text": "is 76 now. He visits every Sunday, rain",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 666.88,
    "end": 676.079,
    "text": "or shine, every single Sunday.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 671.36,
    "end": 679.6,
    "text": "And you know what? It's not enough.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 676.079,
    "end": 683.839,
    "text": "Not because he's not a good son. He's a",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 679.6,
    "end": 687.519,
    "text": "wonderful son. but because no amount of",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 683.839,
    "end": 689.36,
    "text": "time is enough when you truly love",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 687.519,
    "end": 692.399,
    "text": "someone.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 689.36,
    "end": 696.272,
    "text": "Every Sunday when he leaves,  I",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 692.399,
    "end": 699.519,
    "text": "watch him walk to his car and I think,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 696.272,
    "end": 703.44,
    "text": " will I see him again?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 699.519,
    "end": 705.44,
    "text": "At my age, every goodbye might be the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 703.44,
    "end": 708.063,
    "text": "last one.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 705.44,
    "end": 710.64,
    "text": "And that's not morbid. That's just",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 708.063,
    "end": 714.24,
    "text": " mathematics.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 710.64,
    "end": 717.12,
    "text": "But here's what you need to understand.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 714.24,
    "end": 719.12,
    "text": "It's not different for you just because",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 717.12,
    "end": 722.32,
    "text": "you're young.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 719.12,
    "end": 725.68,
    "text": "Every goodbye might be the last one for",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 722.32,
    "end": 727.839,
    "text": "you,  too. You just don't believe",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 725.68,
    "end": 729.6,
    "text": "it yet.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 727.839,
    "end": 731.12,
    "text": "I have a great  great",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 729.6,
    "end": 735.68,
    "text": "granddaughter.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 731.12,
    "end": 738.8,
    "text": "Her name is Sophie. She's 16.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 735.68,
    "end": 741.92,
    "text": "Last month, she came to visit me ",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 738.8,
    "end": 743.839,
    "text": "and she spent the whole time looking at",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 741.92,
    "end": 746.053,
    "text": "her phone",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 743.839,
    "end": 749.76,
    "text": "and I didn't say anything because",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 746.053,
    "end": 752.8,
    "text": " what's the point? She thinks she",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 749.76,
    "end": 756.72,
    "text": "has forever.  She thinks her",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 752.8,
    "end": 760.16,
    "text": "friend's texts are urgent. She thinks",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 756.72,
    "end": 763.76,
    "text": "this moment sitting with her ancient",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 760.16,
    "end": 765.6,
    "text": "great grandmother will always be",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 763.76,
    "end": 770.079,
    "text": "available.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 765.6,
    "end": 773.6,
    "text": "It won't be. And someday, probably when",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 770.079,
    "end": 776.8,
    "text": "she's much older, she'll remember that",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 773.6,
    "end": 779.92,
    "text": "visit. And she'll remember that she",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 776.8,
    "end": 783.12,
    "text": "spent it looking at her phone.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 779.92,
    "end": 786.0,
    "text": "And it will hurt her in ways she can't",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 783.12,
    "end": 789.2,
    "text": "imagine yet. That's what I want to save",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 786.0,
    "end": 790.72,
    "text": "you  from. That pain, that",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 789.2,
    "end": 793.76,
    "text": "regret.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 790.72,
    "end": 797.04,
    "text": "Not the regret of big mistakes. those",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 793.76,
    "end": 800.72,
    "text": "you can make peace with. But the regret",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 797.04,
    "end": 804.72,
    "text": "of simple absence, of being physically",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 800.72,
    "end": 807.04,
    "text": "present, but mentally somewhere else, of",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 804.72,
    "end": 810.16,
    "text": "treating the people you love like",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 807.04,
    "end": 812.079,
    "text": "they'll always be there. They won't",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 810.16,
    "end": 815.12,
    "text": "always be there. ",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 812.079,
    "end": 819.12,
    "text": "I'm not going to be here much longer. I",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 815.12,
    "end": 822.689,
    "text": "can feel it. Not in a scary way, just in",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 819.12,
    "end": 823.04,
    "text": "a knowing way. My body is tired.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 822.689,
    "end": 826.079,
    "text": " ",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 823.04,
    "end": 829.68,
    "text": " It's been working for over a century and",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 826.079,
    "end": 833.279,
    "text": "it's ready to stop. And honestly, I'm",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 829.68,
    "end": 835.789,
    "text": "okay with that. I've had a long life,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 833.279,
    "end": 836.8,
    "text": "much longer than I deserved or expected.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 835.789,
    "end": 838.88,
    "text": "",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 836.8,
    "end": 842.079,
    "text": "But I'm not okay with the thought that",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 838.88,
    "end": 844.72,
    "text": "you might waste yours the way I wasted",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 842.079,
    "end": 848.48,
    "text": "so much of mine.  Because here's",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 844.72,
    "end": 851.199,
    "text": "the truth I learned 70 years too late.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 848.48,
    "end": 854.0,
    "text": "The moments that matter aren't the big",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 851.199,
    "end": 858.0,
    "text": "ones. They're not your wedding day or",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 854.0,
    "end": 860.48,
    "text": "your graduation or your promotion. Those",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 858.0,
    "end": 863.04,
    "text": "are wonderful, but they're not what",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 860.48,
    "end": 866.0,
    "text": "you'll think about at the end. You'll",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 863.04,
    "end": 867.92,
    "text": "think about Tuesday afternoon when your",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 866.0,
    "end": 871.44,
    "text": "dad tried to show you how to fix ",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 867.92,
    "end": 874.72,
    "text": "the sink and you were patient instead of",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 871.44,
    "end": 877.68,
    "text": "annoyed. You'll think about that random",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 874.72,
    "end": 880.56,
    "text": "Saturday morning when you made pancakes",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 877.68,
    "end": 883.36,
    "text": "with your kids and nobody was in a",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 880.56,
    "end": 885.519,
    "text": "hurry. You'll think about the walk you",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 883.36,
    "end": 888.079,
    "text": "took with your husband  when you",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 885.519,
    "end": 892.079,
    "text": "actually listened instead of planning",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 888.079,
    "end": 894.88,
    "text": "what to say next. Those moments, the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 892.079,
    "end": 898.0,
    "text": "ordinary, unglamorous,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 894.88,
    "end": 902.639,
    "text": "utterly unremarkable moments when you",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 898.0,
    "end": 904.959,
    "text": "were just there, fully there.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 902.639,
    "end": 907.76,
    "text": "Those are the ones that matter ",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 904.959,
    "end": 910.88,
    "text": "and they're available to you right now,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 907.76,
    "end": 913.519,
    "text": "today, this  moment. But you have",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 910.88,
    "end": 917.04,
    "text": "to choose them. You have to fight for",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 913.519,
    "end": 919.76,
    "text": "them. Because everything in our world is",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 917.04,
    "end": 923.76,
    "text": "designed to pull you away from them.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 919.76,
    "end": 926.639,
    "text": "Your phone, your work, your ambitions,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 923.76,
    "end": 930.24,
    "text": "your fears,  your endless to-do",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 926.639,
    "end": 933.44,
    "text": "list. If I could go back to 33year-old",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 930.24,
    "end": 936.399,
    "text": "Dorothy standing in that kitchen the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 933.44,
    "end": 939.279,
    "text": "night Robert died, here's what I would",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 936.399,
    "end": 943.68,
    "text": "tell her. The promise you're making",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 939.279,
    "end": 946.24,
    "text": "right now to never waste another day,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 943.68,
    "end": 950.72,
    "text": "you're going to break it. You're going",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 946.24,
    "end": 954.88,
    "text": "to break it over and over again because",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 950.72,
    "end": 957.839,
    "text": "you're human and humans forget.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 954.88,
    "end": 961.04,
    "text": "But here's your real  job.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 957.839,
    "end": 964.56,
    "text": "Remember and return.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 961.04,
    "end": 967.36,
    "text": "Remember and return.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 964.56,
    "end": 970.079,
    "text": "Every time you forget,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 967.36,
    "end": 973.759,
    "text": "every time you drift back  into",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 970.079,
    "end": 977.926,
    "text": "distraction and busyiness and taking",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 973.759,
    "end": 979.92,
    "text": "people for granted, notice it and",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 977.926,
    "end": 982.56,
    "text": " return.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 979.92,
    "end": 985.199,
    "text": "Return to presence.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 982.56,
    "end": 987.68,
    "text": "Return to attention.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 985.199,
    "end": 992.079,
    "text": "Return to love.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 987.68,
    "end": 996.88,
    "text": "Not perfectly, but persistently.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 992.079,
    "end": 999.88,
    "text": "I'm 103 years old. I've been alive for",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 996.88,
    "end": 999.88,
    "text": "37,595",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1001.199,
    "end": 1009.12,
    "text": "days. And  I can count on two",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1004.72,
    "end": 1010.72,
    "text": "hands the number of days I was fully",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1009.12,
    "end": 1013.199,
    "text": "completely",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1010.72,
    "end": 1016.079,
    "text": "utterly present.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1013.199,
    "end": 1019.12,
    "text": "That's my real regret.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1016.079,
    "end": 1022.88,
    "text": "Not that I didn't achieve more or travel",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1019.12,
    "end": 1027.199,
    "text": "more or make more money, but that I",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1022.88,
    "end": 1031.52,
    "text": "sleepwalked through most of my own life.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1027.199,
    "end": 1035.439,
    "text": "Don't do what I did. Don't wait 70 years",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1031.52,
    "end": 1038.88,
    "text": "to learn this. Don't wait until everyone",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1035.439,
    "end": 1041.039,
    "text": "you love is gone to realize you should",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1038.88,
    "end": 1042.48,
    "text": "have loved them better when they were",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1041.039,
    "end": 1044.72,
    "text": "here.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1042.48,
    "end": 1048.72,
    "text": "Stop reading this  and call",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1044.72,
    "end": 1052.559,
    "text": "someone you love. Stop reading this and",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1048.72,
    "end": 1057.36,
    "text": "go sit with someone in silence.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1052.559,
    "end": 1060.16,
    "text": "Stop reading this and look, really look",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1057.36,
    "end": 1063.84,
    "text": "at the people in your life while they're",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1060.16,
    "end": 1067.44,
    "text": "still here to be looked at.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1063.84,
    "end": 1069.28,
    "text": "Because I promise you with everything I",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1067.44,
    "end": 1073.72,
    "text": "have left,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 1069.28,
    "end": 1073.72,
    "text": "later never comes.",
    "textdich": ""
  }
]